00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:07,000
<v sp2>なるほど</v> <v sp2>。</v> <v sp2>３人目</v> <v sp2>。</v>

249
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:11,000
<v sp1>４０３</v> <v sp1>号室の</v>  <v sp1>川原</v>  <v sp1>泰治さん</v> <v sp1>。</v>

